name: Will you die me?
description:
WILL YOU DIE ME?

Take control of Kevin to help him arrive on time to his wedding, surely nothing could go wrong...

CONTROLS

WASD: Movement

THE GAMEDEV.tv GAME JAM 2022

This is a game developed for The GameDev.tv Game Jam 2022.

ENJOY!

Thanks for playing and, please, leave your feedback in a comment!
